653
00:38:44,022 --> 00:38:45,783
All the people you hurt.

654
00:38:45,807 --> 00:38:46,822
I hurt no one.

655
00:38:46,858 --> 00:38:48,119
<i>Heart valves that failed.</i>

656
00:38:48,143 --> 00:38:50,171
The VNS device you put
in an eight-year-old boy

657
00:38:50,195 --> 00:38:51,722
that stopped his heart
over and over again.

658
00:38:51,746 --> 00:38:53,780
<i>I built this company
from nothing.</i>

659
00:38:53,815 --> 00:38:55,398
Abe was overcome with guilt.

660
00:38:55,433 --> 00:38:56,861
- Abe was a coward.
- No, he was

661
00:38:56,885 --> 00:38:58,129
- a hero.
- Abe was gonna destroy

662
00:38:58,153 --> 00:38:59,397
everything that
I sacrificed for.

663
00:38:59,421 --> 00:39:00,669
And you tried to kill him!

664
00:39:00,705 --> 00:39:03,539
I had no choice!

665
00:39:06,411 --> 00:39:08,861
<i>Dad?</i>

666
00:39:08,914 --> 00:39:10,763
Dad?

667
00:39:16,721 --> 00:39:19,505
Earlier today, I...

668
00:39:19,540 --> 00:39:23,009
was admiring your $80,000 Rolex.

669
00:39:24,763 --> 00:39:27,012
It's not often that I
change my watch

670
00:39:27,065 --> 00:39:28,158
in the middle of the day.

671
00:39:28,182 --> 00:39:29,232
Search him.

672
00:39:34,406 --> 00:39:36,139
Who's listening to us?

673
00:39:37,125 --> 00:39:38,691
Who's listening to us?

674
00:39:38,726 --> 00:39:40,259
The FBI.

675
00:39:40,294 --> 00:39:42,479
Son of a bitch.

676
00:39:47,302 --> 00:39:48,918
Bring him.

677
00:39:54,976 --> 00:39:57,160
You're coming with me.

678
00:40:00,215 --> 00:40:02,549
We'll leave through the garage.

679
00:40:04,502 --> 00:40:06,803
FBI! Hands in the air! Freeze!

680
00:40:09,340 --> 00:40:10,890
They've got a hostage!

